"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-news-world-2024-0728-1462213-olympics-seine-pollution\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The first training session for triathletes at the Paris Olympics was scrapped due to pollution in the River Seine, organisers said.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 102, \"end\": 113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following a meeting \\\"on the water quality\\\" and tests, \\\"a joint decision was taken to cancel the swimming part of the triathlon orientation,\\\" a Paris 2024 and World Triathlon statement said.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 0.9999929072713772, \"rank\": 7.0927789664874465e-06, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The River Seine was declared clean enough for swimming in tests from mid-July, but doubts remained as to whether the waters would be fit for competition.\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 328, \"end\": 339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris 2024 and World Triathlon reiterate that the priority is the health of the athletes.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 495, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 0.9999929072713772, \"rank\": 7.0927789664874465e-06, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The analysis carried out yesterday in the Seine showed water quality levels that do not present sufficient guarantees to allow the event to take place,\\\" the statement said.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999999999299007, \"rank\": 5.078526405482564e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers blamed rain in recent days and said they were \\\"confident\\\" water quality would improve enough before the triathlon competition is due to start on 30 July.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the event of heavy rain, untreated sewage can be washed into the river.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the quality is below standards a \\\"Plan B\\\" involves postponing the events for a few days or moving the marathon swimming to Vaires-sur-Marne, on the Marne River east of Paris.\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999884039, \"rank\": 1.1628138035259737e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On 17 July,Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo swam in the Seine along with Paris 2024 chief organiser Tony Estanguet.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 1213, \"end\": 1218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999999999299007, \"rank\": 5.078526405482564e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1230, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.231294714827891e-23, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:AFP  \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1323, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http:/